sql:
SELECT date_recorded, excess_amount, reason
FROM excess_demand
WHERE date_recorded = '2023-05-01';

external_knowledge:
Above-average demand refers to an average demand greater than 20;
The state of 'Bihar' is a specific geographical location in the context of the query;
The first 30 days of data collection refer to the period from day 1 to day 30.

